Scaffold
└── Center
    └── Card
        └── Column
            ├── Image (Movie Poster)
            ├── Text (Movie Title)
            ├── Row
            │   ├── Icon (Star)
            │   └── Text (Movie Rating)
            ├── Text (Movie Language & Genre)
            └── ElevatedButton (Book Tickets)
            
-----------------------------------------------------------

Scaffold – Provides the basic page structure.
Center – Centers the movie ticket card on the screen.
Card – Displays the movie information inside a card with rounded corners and elevation.
Column – Arranges all the widgets vertically.
Image – Shows the movie poster.
Text – Displays the movie title.
Row – Places the rating icon and rating text side by side.
Icon – Displays a star icon for the movie rating.
Text – Shows the movie's language and genre (e.g., "Hindi • Action/Drama").
ElevatedButton – Allows the user to book tickets.
